<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣٤٣- نَصر بْن عَبد الرَّحمَن.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يُحدِّث عَنْ جَدِّه مُعاذ بْن عَفراء.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَالَه شُعبة، عَنْ سَعد،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعتُ نَصر بْن عَبد الرَّحمَن.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>